data.title: Pocahontas Premieres: The Training and Doctrine Command, 7 Cities Brass Band
data.meta_description: See two bands perform at Pocahontas State Park.
data.text:
Date and Time

Saturday, June 8, 2024 from 7:00pm - 8:30pm

Description

The 7 Cities Brass Band performs music from Americaâ€™s newest popular music genre. The eight-piece New Orleans style ensemble performs hits from popular groups such as Youngblood Brass Band, Trombone Shorty, and Bonerama, as well as classic hits from Michael Jackson to Amy Winehouse. The 7 Cities Brass Band plays for schools, festivals, and any community event that requires high-energy popular music. More band info HERE.

Gates open one hour before show time. Admission is free, but parking fees are required at all times. This event is sponsored by Friends of Pocahontas State Park, Stone Brewing Company.
